// BRENN the axeman's starting weapon — a heavy, broad-bladed war axe. Hits harder
// than a soldier's sword but is no finesse tool (modest crit). Sold at the
// HARBORWATCH stores. Reuses the generic blade icon for now.
EquipmentDef(
    id: "battle_axe", name: "BATTLE AXE",
    description: "A broad, heavy war axe that cleaves through guard and mail alike.",
    slot: Weapon, icon: "starter_sword",
    mods: StatMods(attack: 10), crit: 4, accuracy: 2,
)
